dc_description_s: This data represents local health department boundaries for Wisconsin in 2020. [This dataset contains boundaries and attributes of local health departments in the state of Wisconsin. For more information and health officer contact information, please visit the Wisconsin Department of Health Services website: https://www.dhs.wisconsin.gov/lh-depts/counties.htm]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/ddd1345fbccd4fff9ba1dbb2d9949c79_0?geometry=-103.702%2C42.163%2C-75.951%2C47.606
